{"tid":1816460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2020過左一星期，大家有無參與全民議政？","createTime":"2020-01-08T09:04:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T13:10:20.000Z","uid":240448,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2585c76f022d24136c3141426db00d63e9ddc748","tid":1816460,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:04:27.000Z","msg":"2020一開始就唔好過 <br />\n第一日就食哂辣椒噴霧，催淚彈<br />\n又中國肺炎而加美國中東打起上黎 <br />\n<br />\n但記得我地上年大家一齊努力嘅成果<br />\n我地將每個區既區議會反轉左！ <br />\n記得<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好鬆懈</span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好懶</span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好Hea</span></strong> ，<br />\n議會係我地每位香港人努力嘅小小里程碑。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n大家要全民議政，全民監察整個地區工作，<br />\n每個人出一分力，兄弟爬山，各自努力！ </span></strong></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n想提提大家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n1*各位巴絲你地可以去關注你地自己區議員既fb ! <br />\n有咩就inbox 佢地！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>2* 另外可以上<a href=\"https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/cindex.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Fcindex.html&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IvTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=6d8042cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/cindex.html</a><br />\n留意佢地既大型活動同議程<br />\n最近將會舉辦既會議大家都可以搵到 <br />\n例如 1月9號有荃灣區<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VgELcob.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVgELcob.png&h=db3cfde3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zezrGgx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzezrGgx.png&h=50454463&s={SIZE}\" /></strong></span> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>3* 例如中西區上星期傾左咩做左咩<br />\n大家上去就會搵到<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eRTDxok.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeRTDxok.png&h=fba2e352&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jCvZgP1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjCvZgP1.png&h=2fe6b839&s={SIZE}\" /></strong></span> </span><br />\n<br />\n可能各位巴絲發現有更多渠道去參加社區工作同活動<br />\n <ins><em><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎大家share出黎傾下 </span></span></strong><br />\n</em></ins>明白大家都覺得2020 開左個唔好嘅頭<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但係2020 就全靠我地去改變！ <br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">記得唔好鬆懈<br />\n唔好懶<br />\n唔好Hea<br />\n全民議政！</span></span></strong></em><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><br />\n最重要係 <br />\n不分化，兄弟爬山，各自努力！<br />\n唔好忘記每位手足既付出<br />\n願榮光歸香港</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"e52cae7044aaddd6fd86a348c302a63b641baff4","tid":1816460,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:05:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ea159527585e7fbe7f0c3ff61714e7bc08f9b9f6","tid":1816460,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:09:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f9888acafec75afb64c5c3b2920300399a03b6cb","tid":1816460,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:09:58.000Z","msg":"另外<br />\n大家要勤洗手洗手！<br />\n帶口罩！ <br />\n唔舒服儘快睇醫生！"},{"pid":"e5e1f5aa51e68c646eb2c9be6ff26d83d8baf3a4","tid":1816460,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:13:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b0b4b14b109e413fba6cb98511a9146d095e751b","tid":1816460,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:15:58.000Z","msg":"要推"},{"pid":"90d5b9f3ed69eda55ab2f8d5568f5ed470009fcd","tid":1816460,"uid":240448,"like":0,"d